---
import Gradient from "./gradient.astro"
---
<div class="modularity">
    <Gradient src="/gradients/modularity.svg" width="1100" height="873" top={-16}/>
    <h2>
        Empower Your Browser with Gosub's Modularity
    </h2>

    <p>
        Gosub is a browser engine that puts customization at the forefront.
        With its modular design, you can tailor your browsing experience to suit your needs.
        Whether you want to tweak the CSS engine, enhance the HTML parser,
        or optimize the rendering pipeline, Gosub gives you the power to shape your browser.
    </p>

    <div class="modular-items">
        <p>Select your JS engine</p>
        <p>Customizable Rendering pipeline</p>
        <p>Select your JS engine</p>

    </div>
</div>


<style>
    h2 {
        color: white;
        font-size: 3rem;
        width: 45rem;
        text-align: center;
        //margin: 0 auto;
    }

    p {
        width: 60rem;
        color: #DADADA;
        //margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 8.5rem;
    }


    .modularity {
        display: flex;
        position: relative;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;

        height: 50rem;
    }

    .modular-items {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-around;
        width: 55rem;
    }

    .modular-items > p {
        width: 12rem;
    }
</style>